message: /* Buddhi Yoga - Review of a new wiki submission (my first) */ new section

I wrote an article on Fraser and I found another user on Wikipedia has something on her, so I created that page and have now linked this page. Being entirely honest. I know Fraser is a good poet and I did honestly do a bit of self-promotion.

P. Lal wanted to be a Jesuit at one point in his salad days. That fact is not mentioned in this article at all. Nonetheless, this younger Lal became the mature Lal. And literary scholars need to take this into account while assessing him.
